<main style="font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; max-width: 720px; margin: 4rem auto; line-height: 1.6;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 1.2rem;">Square buyer-scoped token minted ✅</h1>
  <p><strong>Saved to the database</strong> — the app now uses it automatically and
    renews it before its ~30-day expiry. No env-var changes needed.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>merchant_id: <%= token["merchant_id"] %></li>
    <li>expires_at: <%= token["expires_at"] %> (auto-refreshed ~3 days ahead)</li>
    <li>scopes are buyer-level only — booking works on Square's free plan</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Re-run this flow only if the refresh token itself is ever revoked
    (e.g. the app's authorization is removed in Square).</p>
</main>
